  <sections>
    <MessageSection>
      <text>Dear Dr Hornfels,</text>
      <size>30</size>
      <italics>false</italics>
      <bold>true</bold>
      <newLines>0</newLines>
      <alignment>Left</alignment>
      <colour>
        <r>0.149019614</r>
        <g>0.149019614</g>
        <b>0.149019614</b>
        <a>1</a>
      </colour>
    </MessageSection>
    <MessageSection>
      <text>While I appreciate your concern with my recent project, I can assure you that the Lumen Extraction System (LES) is completely safe and will not cause undue stress on the mines. While we have yet to do a field test of the device, I have conducted adequate theoretical research to show there is no reasonable doubt towards my claims. I will be resubmitting Form 378-B for field testing approval tomorrow, with Senior Miner Picrite vouching for my claims.</text>
      <size>30</size>
      <italics>false</italics>
      <bold>false</bold>
      <newLines>2</newLines>
      <alignment>Left</alignment>
      <colour>
        <r>0.149019614</r>
        <g>0.149019614</g>
        <b>0.149019614</b>
        <a>1</a>
      </colour>
    </MessageSection>
    <MessageSection>
      <text>In the meantime, perhaps consider making something yourself that works, rather than wasting time and resources on your little pet-project.</text>
      <size>30</size>
      <italics>false</italics>
      <bold>false</bold>
      <newLines>2</newLines>
      <alignment>Left</alignment>
      <colour>
        <r>0.149019614</r>
        <g>0.149019614</g>
        <b>0.149019614</b>
        <a>1</a>
      </colour>
    </MessageSection>
    <MessageSection>
      <text>Sincerely,</text>
      <size>30</size>
      <italics>false</italics>
      <bold>false</bold>
