        <g>0.149019614</g>
        <b>0.149019614</b>
        <a>1</a>
      </colour>
    </MessageSection>
    <MessageSection>
      <text>In the words of my erudite assistant Larimar, ‘That woman is not worth my hi-ho’. Your research is more porous than pumice, and as weighty as it too. If the committee shares even half a braincell between them, and Chert Picrite doesn’t poison their minds, they will see that your endeavours are entirely too dangerous, not to mention morally reprehensible. </text>
      <size>30</size>
      <italics>false</italics>
      <bold>false</bold>
      <newLines>2</newLines>
      <alignment>Left</alignment>
      <colour>
        <r>0.149019614</r>
        <g>0.149019614</g>
        <b>0.149019614</b>
        <a>1</a>
      </colour>
    </MessageSection>
    <MessageSection>
      <text>I hope you perish in a fire, alongside every last one of your corrupt inventions.</text>
      <size>30</size>
